8 An Act relating to controlled dangerous substances;
amending 63 O.S. 2021, Sections 2-315 and 2-508,
9 which relate to destruction of controlled dangerous
substances and disposition of seized property;
10 authorizing destruction of controlled dangerous
substances by certain individuals; removing
11 requirement for submission to destroy controlled
dangerous substances; removing incineration
12 requirement; requiring destruction of controlled
dangerous substances be in compliance with certain
13 federal regulations; removing requirement for certain
site; updating statutory language; updating statutory
14 references; and providing an effective date.
